{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Santiago Ferreira","author":"Santiago Ferreira"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"4caa944a-16e1-51c7-834a-056993346745","excerpt":"Cross platform, cloud enabled animation + design AppThis is an ongoing personal project. It’s goal is to make it easy to create good looking animated visuals…","html":"<h3>Cross platform, cloud enabled animation + design App</h3>\n<p>This is an ongoing personal project. It’s goal is to make it easy to create good looking animated visuals anywhere and to be able to export them to any format. The app runs on <strong>iOS</strong>, <strong>Android</strong> and <strong>Web</strong> and user data is synchronized across devices via <strong>AWS DataStore</strong>. Video encoding is implemented on-device with an <strong>AWS Lambda</strong> fallback for incompatible devices or browsers.</p>\n<p>Graphics are implemented in <strong>PIXI.js</strong> which provides fast, hardware accelerated, performance. Moreover, several elements such as backgrounds are implemented as <strong>WebGL Shaders</strong>.</p>\n\n  <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/ac2210455a1dea2f4386479f1c6ef852/20539/design_anywhere_export_everywhere.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n  \n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 1360px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 67.06204379562044%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <picture>\n        <source srcset=\"/static/ac2210455a1dea2f4386479f1c6ef852/53e9f/design_anywhere_export_everywhere.webp 340w,\n/static/ac2210455a1dea2f4386479f1c6ef852/0991f/design_anywhere_export_everywhere.webp 680w,\n/static/ac2210455a1dea2f4386479f1c6ef852/9d77c/design_anywhere_export_everywhere.webp 1360w,\n/static/ac2210455a1dea2f4386479f1c6ef852/27063/design_anywhere_export_everywhere.webp 2040w,\n/static/ac2210455a1dea2f4386479f1c6ef852/7cfdf/design_anywhere_export_everywhere.webp 2192w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1360px) 100vw, 1360px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n        <source srcset=\"/static/ac2210455a1dea2f4386479f1c6ef852/a2595/design_anywhere_export_everywhere.png 340w,\n/static/ac2210455a1dea2f4386479f1c6ef852/2473e/design_anywhere_export_everywhere.png 680w,\n/static/ac2210455a1dea2f4386479f1c6ef852/55534/design_anywhere_export_everywhere.png 1360w,\n/static/ac2210455a1dea2f4386479f1c6ef852/0a656/design_anywhere_export_everywhere.png 2040w,\n/static/ac2210455a1dea2f4386479f1c6ef852/20539/design_anywhere_export_everywhere.png 2192w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1360px) 100vw, 1360px\" type=\"image/png\">\n        <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" src=\"/static/ac2210455a1dea2f4386479f1c6ef852/55534/design_anywhere_export_everywhere.png\" alt=\"design anywhere export everywhere\" title>\n      </picture>\n      </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    \n<hr>\n<h4>Minimal, intuitive and powerful UI</h4>\n<div class=\"sntx-markdown-21cols-parent\">\n  <video preload=\"metadata\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" controls poster=\"/video-posters/ui_01.jpg\">\n    <source src=\"/ui_01-d1d716b0f0895b9660c8993bfb02f231.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n    Your browser does not support the video tag.\n  </video>\n  <p>Select an element and the bottom bar automatically updates with the necessary controls. UI controls are minimal yet they display all the information you need while editing. For example: Use colored sliders to colorize elements, use animation select buttons to select among animation options.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sntx-markdown-21cols-parent\">\n  <video preload=\"metadata\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" controls poster=\"/video-posters/grid_menus.jpg\">\n    <source src=\"/grid_menus-581bd9053a8ace10b915e6ec945e975b.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n    Your browser does not support the video tag.\n  </video>\n  <p>Grid menus make it simple to browse and insert elements into the artwork. They can also be used to access saved artworks.</p>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<h4>Color Palette system</h4>\n<div class=\"sntx-markdown-21cols-parent\">\n  <video preload=\"metadata\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" controls poster=\"/video-posters/palettes.jpg\">\n    <source src=\"/palettes-d50711df0fe028d78a144faa3bdb52a2.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n    Your browser does not support the video tag.\n  </video>\n  <p>Artwork colors and related UI adapt to a global color palette. This makes it easy to select color combinations that work out of the box. Moreover, color palettes can be changed at any point in time, making it easy to create variations of artworks. Related UI, such as color sliders automatically update to the current selected palette.</p>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<h4>Stretchable artwork</h4>\n<div class=\"sntx-markdown-21cols-parent\">\n  <video preload=\"metadata\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" controls poster=\"/video-posters/aspect_ratio.jpg\">\n    <source src=\"/aspect_ratio-13e80b086d617d83fca8472ca60b6426.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n    Your browser does not support the video tag.\n  </video>\n  <p>Artworks automatically stretch to fit different aspect ratios. This makes it easy to export to multiple targets, for example: 9:16 (Instagram story), 1:1 (Facebook post), 16:9 (YouTube video).</p>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<h4>Generative design tools</h4>\n<p>Use generative design to create elements. The following example shows a flower generator with different parameters. By adjusting parameters with buttons and sliders, users can create endless variations of animated shapes, backgrounds and other design elements.</p>\n<div class=\"sntx-markdown-2cols-parent\">\n  <video preload=\"metadata\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" controls poster=\"/video-posters/flowers01.jpg\">\n    <source src=\"/flowers01-398fce2306fb3b9ae728383d51ca4522.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n    Your browser does not support the video tag.\n  </video>\n  <video preload=\"metadata\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" controls poster=\"/video-posters/flowers02.jpg\">\n    <source src=\"/flowers02-c7d90b9d024bd675e42b1da62b7d0b69.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n    Your browser does not support the video tag.\n  </video>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sntx-markdown-3cols-parent\">\n  \n  <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/d863658cb53b136e6895ea4925f82b6e/9337e/flowers02.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n  \n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 1360px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <picture>\n        <source srcset=\"/static/d863658cb53b136e6895ea4925f82b6e/53e9f/flowers02.webp 340w,\n/static/d863658cb53b136e6895ea4925f82b6e/0991f/flowers02.webp 680w,\n/static/d863658cb53b136e6895ea4925f82b6e/9d77c/flowers02.webp 1360w,\n/static/d863658cb53b136e6895ea4925f82b6e/f3eb5/flowers02.webp 1522w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1360px) 100vw, 1360px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n        <source srcset=\"/static/d863658cb53b136e6895ea4925f82b6e/a2595/flowers02.png 340w,\n/static/d863658cb53b136e6895ea4925f82b6e/2473e/flowers02.png 680w,\n/static/d863658cb53b136e6895ea4925f82b6e/55534/flowers02.png 1360w,\n/static/d863658cb53b136e6895ea4925f82b6e/9337e/flowers02.png 1522w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1360px) 100vw, 1360px\" type=\"image/png\">\n        <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" src=\"/static/d863658cb53b136e6895ea4925f82b6e/55534/flowers02.png\" alt=\"flowers02\" title>\n      </picture>\n      </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    \n  \n  <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/d70f4d26ede5feab14e04d0a9d1092b6/9337e/flowers01.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n  \n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 1360px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <picture>\n        <source srcset=\"/static/d70f4d26ede5feab14e04d0a9d1092b6/53e9f/flowers01.webp 340w,\n/static/d70f4d26ede5feab14e04d0a9d1092b6/0991f/flowers01.webp 680w,\n/static/d70f4d26ede5feab14e04d0a9d1092b6/9d77c/flowers01.webp 1360w,\n/static/d70f4d26ede5feab14e04d0a9d1092b6/f3eb5/flowers01.webp 1522w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1360px) 100vw, 1360px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n        <source srcset=\"/static/d70f4d26ede5feab14e04d0a9d1092b6/a2595/flowers01.png 340w,\n/static/d70f4d26ede5feab14e04d0a9d1092b6/2473e/flowers01.png 680w,\n/static/d70f4d26ede5feab14e04d0a9d1092b6/55534/flowers01.png 1360w,\n/static/d70f4d26ede5feab14e04d0a9d1092b6/9337e/flowers01.png 1522w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1360px) 100vw, 1360px\" type=\"image/png\">\n        <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" src=\"/static/d70f4d26ede5feab14e04d0a9d1092b6/55534/flowers01.png\" alt=\"flowers01\" title>\n      </picture>\n      </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    \n  \n  <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/d0d4e337c40a4b08875f1cbba063bd86/9337e/flowers03.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n  \n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 1360px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <picture>\n        <source srcset=\"/static/d0d4e337c40a4b08875f1cbba063bd86/53e9f/flowers03.webp 340w,\n/static/d0d4e337c40a4b08875f1cbba063bd86/0991f/flowers03.webp 680w,\n/static/d0d4e337c40a4b08875f1cbba063bd86/9d77c/flowers03.webp 1360w,\n/static/d0d4e337c40a4b08875f1cbba063bd86/f3eb5/flowers03.webp 1522w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1360px) 100vw, 1360px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n        <source srcset=\"/static/d0d4e337c40a4b08875f1cbba063bd86/a2595/flowers03.png 340w,\n/static/d0d4e337c40a4b08875f1cbba063bd86/2473e/flowers03.png 680w,\n/static/d0d4e337c40a4b08875f1cbba063bd86/55534/flowers03.png 1360w,\n/static/d0d4e337c40a4b08875f1cbba063bd86/9337e/flowers03.png 1522w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1360px) 100vw, 1360px\" type=\"image/png\">\n        <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" src=\"/static/d0d4e337c40a4b08875f1cbba063bd86/55534/flowers03.png\" alt=\"flowers03\" title>\n      </picture>\n      </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    \n</div>\n<hr>\n<h4>Animated colors</h4>\n<p>Since colors are dynamic, they can be manipulated and animated by selecting and tweaking different parameters.</p>\n<div class=\"sntx-markdown-2cols-parent\">\n  <video preload=\"metadata\" width=\"100%\" controls poster=\"/video-posters/colorizer_tiger.jpg\">\n    <source src=\"/colorizer_tiger-8af474a21b739e33001a71e860d0db3d.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n    Your browser does not support the video tag.\n  </video>\n  <video preload=\"metadata\" width=\"100%\" controls poster=\"/video-posters/colorizier_butterfly.jpg\">\n    <source src=\"/colorizier_butterfly-1eac3a902d50e88cb7fbc7c01d2397d2.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n    Your browser does not support the video tag.\n  </video>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<h4>Synchronized to music</h4>\n<p>The timeline and all animations are synchronized to a global BPM (beats per minute) value. Just add a song and the artwork will be moving along to the beat.</p>\n  <video preload=\"metadata\" width=\"100%\" controls poster=\"/video-posters/music_sync.jpg\">\n    <source src=\"/music_sync-c71776bf7267556b58c5df62cb922718.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n    Your browser does not support the video tag.\n  </video>","frontmatter":{"title":"Animated Design App","date":"January 25, 2021","description":"Cross platform, cloud enabled animation + design App","technologies":["React Native","PIXI.js","AWS","TypeScript","Node.js"],"thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":2,"src":"/static/181bd7d595d99ffa8871266544c264d5/41d74/jinnix-cover-horizontal-01.png","srcSet":"/static/181bd7d595d99ffa8871266544c264d5/fa754/jinnix-cover-horizontal-01.png 340w,\n/static/181bd7d595d99ffa8871266544c264d5/1bf7a/jinnix-cover-horizontal-01.png 680w,\n/static/181bd7d595d99ffa8871266544c264d5/41d74/jinnix-cover-horizontal-01.png 1360w,\n/static/181bd7d595d99ffa8871266544c264d5/dc9f7/jinnix-cover-horizontal-01.png 2000w","sizes":"(max-width: 1360px) 100vw, 1360px"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/animated-design/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/project-management/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Project management app"}},"next":null}}